<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Présentation - Plinkk</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e2f, #252540);
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 800px;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 255, 200, 0.5);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #00ffc8;
      text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 200, 0.7);
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #e0e0e0;
    }

    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .buttons a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      background: #00ffc8;
      color: #111;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .buttons a:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 200, 0.7);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #aaa;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Bienvenue sur Plinkk</h1>
    <p>
      Plinkk est une alternative moderne à Linktree.  
      Minimaliste, rapide et entièrement personnalisable,  
      il vous permet de partager vos liens, réseaux sociaux  
      et ressources dans une page unique, élégante et responsive.
    </p>
    <div class="buttons">
        <a href="marvideo">Voir la démo</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/Klaynight-dev/plinkk" target="_blank">Code source (Plinkk)</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/Marvideo2009/plinkk-backend" target="_blank">Code source (Plinkk Backend)</a>
    </div>
    <footer>
      © 2025 - Plinkk Backend, sous licence MIT
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>